<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Temple</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is surrounded by a number of important routes including 52 Street E on the west, 32 Avenue N on the south, 68 Street E on the east and the McKnight Boulevard on the north that connect it to the rest of the city.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Temple comprise an eclectic mix of single-family detached and attached units, townhouses and low rise apartment condos that are readily available at an average price of $330,000. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Regardless of whether you are a first time home buyer or an experienced real estate investor, the community in Temple will appeal to people from all walks of life. </p>
        </div>
